title.rendered: STEDI SUZUKI JIMNY (JB64W/JB74W) PIGGY BACK ADAPTOR

content.rendered:
Suzuki Jimny (JB64W/JB74W) Driving Light Piggy Back High Beam Adapter

DETAILS

Specifically designed to suit the Suzuki Jimny (JB64W/JB74W).

The easy solution for wiring up your Driving Lights with no need for splicing, trapping or soldering as it is a direct Plug & Play install.

Designed to work with all STEDI Quick Fit Wiring Harnesses.

 

SPECIFICATIONS

CONNECTOR TYPE 6 Pin
FITS SUZUKI JIMNY 2018+

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1 x Suzuki Jimny (JB64W/JB74W) High beam Adapter
